rComments: Professor Yehudai is a really terrific professor. I dont normally write reviews (positive or negative) for professors unless they really deserve it. I took two courses with professor Yehudai this year. He was a great lecturer in both. You will learn lots if you show up to class and pay attention. Doing the readings are a good idea!

Go to his office hours, he really wants to hear from you. He is very balanced on a subject that ignite a lot of passion and unfortunately a lot heated discussions. That was the case in this academic class. Awesome prof. A decent grader. A lot of reading which he expects to be done when the time comes to participate.
A great teacher! Cares a lot about his students. Teaches the material thoroughly and in an engaging manner. Do your readings because class participation counts for grades. Would highly recommend!
